"A.P.238/4/9/12:00": "It seems the photons have changed. The end of this must be ahead."
"Before we go to the next area, there's something that I wanted to ask you."
"There were any number of other people you could have partnered with, right?"
"You don't need to say anything, I can tell by the look on your face."
"I don't mean to insult you or anything by pointing this out."
"It's that I wanted to thank you. I've had a lot of fun."
"I didn't really intend to participate in the first place, and teaming up with someone..."
"Well, normally it has nothing to do with me."
"Sorry I got side tracked. Let's go finish this."
